Package parser.interfaces

This package holds all of the interfaces used in the parser. They are all placed in this package so that they are easy to find.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Condition
    This interface contains methods used for evaluating] and getting the type of any condition used in the parser.
    Exec
    This is used to delineate any classes that are executed instead of evaluated in teh parser.
    Number
    This class is used to represent any number that the user wants to store in the parser.
    Validator
    This interface is used to delineate any classes (in the parser) that can be validated.
    Value
    Interface containing methods for all classed that contain a value
